OL,7,FThe debate sparked by Kim Leadbeater
OL,8,FMP's private members' bill has huge
OL,9,Fconsequences for the hospice sector,
OL,10,FITV News UK Editor Paul Brand reports
OL,12,FAt Royal Trinity Hospice, they deal
OL,13,Fwith death on a daily basis.
OL,15,FBut when I visited this week, I was
OL,16,Fsurprised by how much life there is to
OL,17,Fthe place too.
