OL,7,F"We had our wedding anniversary a few
OL,8,Fdays ago on October 26. I was keeping
OL,9,Fmy fingers crossed that he would pass
OL,10,Fthat date and yes, we have been
OL,11,Fmarried for 46 years."
OL,13,F"It's up to him. Because he's in a lot
OL,14,Fof pain. As long as he's kept
OL,15,Fcomfortable right up to the end,
OL,16,Fthat's all I wish for him," she tells
OL,17,Fme.
