OL,7,FYet in the same hospice, dealing with
OL,8,Fthe same patients, I meet Dr Samantha
OL,9,FLund. She says assisted dying is
OL,10,Frarely raised with her in her medical
OL,11,Frole.
OL,13,FAnd like the majority of palliative
OL,14,Fcare doctors in the UK, she would
OL,15,Foppose it because of the risk it might
OL,16,Fpose to vulnerable patients.
OL,18,F"For me, this was brought massively
OL,19,Finto focus recently when my mum died,"
OL,20,Fshe tells me.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
