OL,3,CHospice staff are experts in death,
OL,4,Cbut they are divided over assisted
OL,5,Cdying
OL,7,F"Whenever my mum was asked what
OL,8,Fworried her, she would say about the
OL,9,Fimpact of her illness on her family.
OL,10,FAnd I worry if assisted dying had been
OL,11,Flegalised she would have felt a
OL,12,Fpressure to consider it."
OL,14,FThat is not the only worry for some in
OL,15,Fthe hospice sector.
OL,17,FIn other countries that have legalised
OL,18,Fassisted dying, hospices have been
OL,19,Fobliged to facilitate assisted deaths,
OL,20,Fin some cases losing their funding if
OL,21,Fthey don't.
