OL,7,FA report by the Health Select
OL,8,FCommittee in Parliament this year did
OL,9,Fnot find evidence that palliative care
OL,10,Fhas suffered in countries that have
OL,11,Fintroduced assisted dying.
OL,13,FBut the sector here faces a funding
OL,14,Fcrisis, and some worry that assisted
OL,15,Fdying will overtake any focus on
OL,16,Fimproving hospice care as a first
OL,17,Fpriority.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
