OL,3,CHospice staff are experts in death,
OL,4,Cbut they are divided over assisted
OL,5,Cdying
OL,7,FHospice UK, which represents hundreds
OL,8,Fof hospices across the country, is
OL,9,Fremaining neutral, while asking not to
OL,10,Fbe forgotten in the debate.
OL,12,FCharlie King from Hospice UK told me:
OL,13,F"Hospice staff, volunteers and of
OL,14,Fcourse patients have crucial
OL,15,Fexperience and expertise to bring to
OL,16,Fthis debate.
OL,18,F"It is so important that they are
OL,19,Flistened to by politicians as the
OL,20,Fcountry considers the legislation on
OL,21,Fassisted dying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
