OL,3,CHospice staff are experts in death,
OL,4,Cbut they are divided over assisted
OL,5,Cdying
OL,7,F"As Hospice UK we are neutral on a
OL,8,Fchange in the law. But we can all
OL,9,Fagree it is intolerable that anyone
OL,10,Fmight feel they need to choose an
OL,11,Fassisted death for fear of not getting
OL,12,Fthe care they need at end of life.
OL,14,F"Yet currently, the hospice sector is
OL,15,Funder severe financial pressure. We'd
OL,16,Furge all MPs to back the need for
OL,17,Freform of how we fund palliative and
OL,18,Fend of life care in the UK."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
