OL,7,FThe assisted dying bill will be
OL,8,Fdebated and voted on by MPs on
OL,9,FNovember 29.
OL,11,FIf it passes, it will be the biggest
OL,12,Fsocial change in Britain in
OL,13,Fgenerations.
OL,15,FIt will fundamentally alter our
OL,16,Frelationship with death, even for
OL,17,Fthose in the hospice sector who are
OL,18,Falready well acquainted with it.
